<span id="Item_descriptions"></span>
=== Descrições dos Itens ===

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
The promotional video showed the '''Festival Gate''' as a traditional [[wikipedia:Paifang|paifang]] that served as a portal. The '''Good Fortune Coin''' carried a horse design and could be flipped. The '''Firecrackers''' were interactive and produced explosions. The '''Pellet Drum''' (also called a [[wikipedia:Pellet drum|den-den daiko]]) could be spun to produce sound. The '''Lucky Lantern''' surrounded [[Special:MyLanguage/Warp Effects|warp]] with a swirl of floating lanterns as the user appeared or disappeared.<ref name="yt-lny"/>
</div>

